A test case has been added.

``` javascript
focus: {
            // Fire native event if possible so blur/focus sequence is correct
            trigger: function() {
                var focusTrigger = function() {
                    if ( this !== document.activeElement && this.focus ) {
                        this.focus();
                        return false;
                    }
                };

                if ( document.readyState !== "complete" ) {
